            "section_heading": "Returns",
            "content": "<ul><li>Returns are accepted on full-price pieces purchased directly from Diamension (online or retail), if they are unworn, in original condition, and returned within 14 days of delivery.</li><li>For hygiene reasons, earrings cannot be returned.</li><li>Custom, bespoke, engraved, or made-to-order pieces are final sale and cannot be returned.</li><li>Returns that do not meet these conditions will be sent back to the customer.</li><li>Once approved, store credits are issued in the form of a Diamension gift card, valid for 3 years across our website and retail stores.</li></ul><p>To request a return, please contact our team at care@diamension.com.</p>",
