          "settings": {
            "section_heading": "Repairs",
            "content": "<p>We stand by the quality of our craftsmanship and offer repair services should your piece need attention.</p><ul><li>To initiate a repair, please email care@diamension.com with your order details.</li><li>Items must be returned in their original or secure protective packaging to avoid damage in transit.</li><li>Repair fees may apply depending on the service required. Shipping charges for repairs are borne by the client.</li><li>For international customers, repair shipping and duties will be calculated and confirmed prior to servicing.</li></ul><p>If the item does not meet our return/repair guidelines upon arrival, it will be sent back at the customer's expense.</p>",
