            "content": "<p>As part of our sustainability promise, we encourage customers to recycle their old or broken Diamension pieces.</p><ul><li>Jewellery with at least 80% of its original material may be eligible for our recycling program.</li><li>Store credits are offered based on material value (assessed by our team).</li><li>Proof of purchase is required to determine the credit value. Without proof, a fixed recycling credit will be applied.</li><li>Diamension reserves the right to decline recycling requests if the condition does not meet our guidelines.</li></ul>",
